dc_title_s: Hopkins Marine Station, Pacific Grove, California, 2001
dc_description_s: This raster layer is a georeferenced image (GeoTIFF) of an aerial photograph of Hopkins Marine Station, located near Monterey Bay in Pacific Grove, California. This layer is part of a collection of data relating to Hopkins Marine Station located near Monterey Bay, California.These data are intended for researchers, students, policy makers, and the general public for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production.
